title: Coronavirus update: China 'seriously concerned' about Australia's call for outbreak investigation
description: China dismisses Australia's questioning of how Beijing handled the coronavirus pandemic, saying Foreign Minister Marise Payne's calls for an international investigation are "not based on facts".
